There is also a more insidious suspicion that the ANC is trying to delay the
issue of the licences in order to allow various US and Scandinavian
companies to participate when sanctions in those countries are lifted. There
have even been unsubstantiated suggestions that the ANC expects financial
contributions from successful bidders.
